Benefits.FeatureTitle: All the taste, in half the time
Benefits.Name: All the taste, in half the time
Benefits.DisplayName: All the taste, in half the time
Benefits.Description: The CombiQuick oven is the faster way to exceptional flavours and exciting dishes, combining hot air fan cooking with the speed of a microwave to give you the mouth-watering finish and textures of a conventional oven in one compact space. From now on, time is no longer an obstacle to taste.

Benefits.Name: Multi-function Oven
Benefits.Description: This multi-function oven offers both fan forced and conventional cooking options, so you can get the best results from whatever youre cooking.

Benefits.Name: Automatic weight defrost program
Benefits.Description: The total defrost time is automatically calculated by allocating variable defrost power levels at each stage of the defrost cycle.

Benefits.Name: Quick Start
Benefits.Description: By pressing the start button you can activate the 30 seconds program and get 30 seconds of cooking at a high power level.

Benefits.Name: SteamBoost
Benefits.Description: SteamBoost works in exactly the same way as a traditional cooking methods, with the added benefit of steam. Locking in the natural moisture to deliver a whole range of juicy and succulent dishes including meat, fish, casseroles and vegetables  even desserts. Its all about taste, and lots of it.

Benefits.FeatureTitle: Rare. Medium. Well done.  At your command with SenseCook
Benefits.Name: Rare. Medium. Well done.  At your command with SenseCook
Benefits.DisplayName: Rare. Medium. Well done.  At your command with SenseCook
Benefits.Description: Your personal sous chef. Use the Food Sensor to tell the oven how you want your dish cooked  using just the words you would in a restaurant  rare, medium, or well done. Without even opening the oven door, everything from tender joints of meat to molten chocolate fondants are controlled and mastered.  At last, an oven that speaks your language.

Benefits.Description: Ensuring a perfect match for your compact oven with complementary Command Wheel. Without other buttons creating a busy dashboard, the Command Wheel makes the UI simple and streamlined for perfection on a plate, every time.

Fragments.InternalFormat: Not sure how to bake in a convection oven to host big groups? This InfiSpace™ 72-litre oven comes with three baking levels for multi baking options. Smooth enamel interior makes cleaning a breeze.

Benefits.FeatureTitle: Perfect amount of steam for every dish
Benefits.Name: Perfect amount of steam for every dish
Benefits.DisplayName: Perfect amount of steam for every dish
Benefits.Description: The advanced humidity sensor continuously measures and automatically adjusts temperature and moisture levels in the oven to suit the type of food you are cooking when using low, medium and high humidity cooking functions.  As food generates its own humidity, and some more than others, it adjusts the amount of steam required in the cavity to deliver precisely the right amount of humidity. This not only leads to more efficient water usage, but ensures that every dish is cooked to perfection.

Benefits.Name: Turn flavour up to full
Benefits.Description: The SteamBoost oven with full steam makes more from the flavours in your food.  It works in exactly the same way as a traditional oven, with the added benefit of steam. The introduction of steam makes all the difference. Locking in the natural moisture to deliver a whole range of juicy and succulent dishes including meat, fish, casseroles and vegetables  even desserts. Its all about taste, and lots of it.

Benefits.FeatureTitle: Master even the most complex flavours.
Benefits.Name: Master even the most complex flavours.
Benefits.DisplayName: Master even the most complex flavours.
Benefits.Description: Every meal should be an experience.  With that in mind we created the SteamPro oven with full steam.  It has three cooking modes - heat, steam, and a combination of both. In the combination mode it will calculate exactly the right combination of heat and steam automatically. Whether you're roasting or grilling meats, baking bread, creating delicate desserts or using the SousVide feature as seen in many professional restaurants around the world, you can be confident your cooking will be elevated to another level.

Benefits.Name: SousVide in just 4 steps
Benefits.Description: Prepare, seal, cook and serve dishes with the ultimate control and perfect results every time. Even the most delicate food can be cooked to perfection using low temperature steam cooking from 95C to as low as 50C with 1C adjustability.

Features.Name: An Integrated SousVide cooking system

Benefits.Name: FamilySafe Doors
Benefits.Description: For extra peace of mind and safety in the kitchen, we've developed multi-layer glazed oven doors. Given the multi-layer glazing, the Westinghouse FamilySafe oven doors are found to be cooler and safer for families with young children.

Benefits.FeatureTitle: Room for everything with FamilySize Ovens
Benefits.Name: Room for everything with FamilySize Ovens
Benefits.DisplayName: Room for everything with FamilySize Ovens
Benefits.Description: Whether it's a big family gathering or a simple Sunday roast, you'll love Westinghouse Family Size ovens, our huge 80-litre gross capacity ovens with room for everything.  The home cook's delight, the impressive width makes it super easy to get things in and out of the oven. Plus it can also fit even the largest turkey or lamb roast, so you'll never have to worry about not fitting food in. Add in A-Class energy efficiency to European standards, low heat emissions and a super quiet operation, and you have all the ingredients for the perfect oven.

Benefits.Name: Fingerprint resistant stainless steel
Benefits.Description: Fingerprints have met their match. Enjoy a family-friendly oven with stainless steel that really is stainless. It's effortless to keep your oven looking like new with our easy-to-clean, smudge-free stainless steel.

Benefits.Name: Effortless baking
Benefits.Description: Adding steam to your Baking Program can lift your baking skills to a whole new level. The Bake +Steam function on this oven uses a touch of steam to create a richer and glossier colour, a crispier crust and soft delicious texture for your home-baked goodies.

Benefits.Name: Say hello to intuitive control
Benefits.Description: Cooking should be fun, not complicated. Our Intuitive Oven Interface (IOI) gives you a simpler and more enjoyable way to cook. You wont even need a manual.

Benefits.Name: The perfect result, every time
Benefits.Description: The Smart Food Probe ensures your dishes are delicious every time. The food probe alerts you when food reaches the desired core temperature and switches the oven off so you get the perfect result.

Benefits.Name: Smooth operator
Benefits.Description: Our fully extendable telescopic runners give you safe, effortless access to all areas of your oven. This makes it simple to turn, baste and check on your food for delicious results every time.

Features.Name: Surround lighting for better illumination
Features.Description: Keeping an eye on your delicious food couldnt be simpler, with halogen lights embedded in the front and back to illuminate the oven.
